I ran this through a Frequency Analysis and it looks like a classic MP3, but the DB drop off point makes it look more like a 
MiniDisc. I was told that was originally an MD recording, so I included a FA screen for you all to look at and judge. It&#039;s sad
that 8 years later I&#039;m finding I got fucked on a lot of trades by worthless MP3 burns. This was also not done as DAO, so it has
clicks between tracks which further makes me think it&#039;s MP3 sourced. You be the judge.
